properties.Name: MedicalInformationBureauReport
properties.Description: A report supplied by the Medical Information Bureau, which is a non-profit central information agency established by a group of insurance companies to consolidate and share information about applicants.

Columns.Name: MibReportStatement
Columns.Description: A statement, comments or additional information regarding the MIB report.

Columns.Name: InsurancePolicyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Insurance Policy.

Columns.Name: InsurancePercentageOfSalary
Columns.Description: The amount of insurance as a percentage of annual salary provided under the associated Benefit Components.
